description: Oh my goodness, this too-cool-for-school bus is rocking the streets of Rocklin with its amazing variety of frozen treats!A few of their delightful goodies include Root Beer Floats, Dole Whips, Frozen Yogurt, and Shaved Ice too. You are also sure to find all your favorite flavors as well as every kind of top-notch topping. For all this and more, be sure to keep an eye out for this bus because you simply must make your day complete with a tasty sweet from OMG! Yogurt.
name: OMG! Yogurt
